                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1280-18440408 t18440408-1280-punishment-200"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
               </p>
